data.description: ** HIGHLY UPGRADED! ** METICULOUSLY MAINTAINED! **  This spacious 5 bedroom home is located in the respected Tule Springs gated community.  The interior showcases a modern open concept floor plan, tile flooring, ceiling fans, and custom window treatments throughout.  Enjoy your designer kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, upgraded tall cabinetry, and a spacious walk in pantry.  Head upstairs to an oversized loft for additional living space and a spectacular master retreat. The backyard is fully landscaped with pavers, turf, and showcases a built in patio cover to comfortably entertain guests. The garage is fully finished and has a 220v hookup for electric vehicle charging. Conveniently located nearby freeway access and shopping. This home is CLEAN and shows very well. Schedule a showing today! We look forward to seeing you.
